  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/1425cfb4041f6d1f8d978109d2fcd551.webp?t=1749555056\" width=600 height=49 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/496ec3b66678d7da8450400f80c4b77a.poster.avif?t=1749555056\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/496ec3b66678d7da8450400f80c4b77a.webm?t=1749555056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/496ec3b66678d7da8450400f80c4b77a.mp4?t=1749555056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Embark on an immersive journey in post-apocalyptic Stillwater Bay, where narrative-driven gameplay unfolds through interactions with engaging NPCs and missions. <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/9f7ca1bf50eff816d8f55f780b7405c8.webp?t=1749555056\" width=600 height=49 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/86c2bf1b3f23e1d6c3b1955f12fd707b.poster.avif?t=1749555056\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/86c2bf1b3f23e1d6c3b1955f12fd707b.webm?t=1749555056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/86c2bf1b3f23e1d6c3b1955f12fd707b.mp4?t=1749555056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Gear up for a challenge, where you'll navigate through intense encounters that promise an adrenaline-fueled experience, requiring a perfect blend of skill and strategy. Get ready for each encounter to put you on the edge of your seat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/940e7f2e0f7812e772f81b754588f0f8.webp?t=1749555056\" width=600 height=49 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/0ac97ad1f8b2cc958afbcd235e0cc1d0.poster.avif?t=1749555056\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/0ac97ad1f8b2cc958afbcd235e0cc1d0.webm?t=1749555056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/0ac97ad1f8b2cc958afbcd235e0cc1d0.mp4?t=1749555056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your own base, streamline your resource usage, and survive the apocalypse in style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/66b064c9e9dc4d956ff23da88f129826.webp?t=1749555056\" width=600 height=49 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/9d4ac025b91665f391f10c4e1cd121ea.poster.avif?t=1749555056\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/9d4ac025b91665f391f10c4e1cd121ea.webm?t=1749555056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/9d4ac025b91665f391f10c4e1cd121ea.mp4?t=1749555056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Navigate the challenging terrain of Stillwater Bay, where survival hinges on your ability to loot essential gear, water, and food. Immerse yourself in the exhilarating quest for sustenance and supplies, turning every exploration into a pulse-pounding adventure where your survival instincts and strategic looting are key. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/28195e68375efc9792197c0ecd49f9cf.webp?t=1749555056\" width=600 height=49 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/2bf0856d04384a984a559da0f1fd0471.poster.avif?t=1749555056\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/2bf0856d04384a984a559da0f1fd0471.webm?t=1749555056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/2bf0856d04384a984a559da0f1fd0471.mp4?t=1749555056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Forge your character's destiny through exhilarating progression. Level up, conquer missions, and equip new gear while strategically assigning stat points to tailor your playstyle. Dive into a dynamic gaming experience where each choice molds a unique and personalized journey of survival and domination over your opponents. </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/1425cfb4041f6d1f8d978109d2fcd551.webp?t=1749555056\" width=600 height=49 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/496ec3b66678d7da8450400f80c4b77a.poster.avif?t=1749555056\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/496ec3b66678d7da8450400f80c4b77a.webm?t=1749555056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/496ec3b66678d7da8450400f80c4b77a.mp4?t=1749555056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Embark on an immersive journey in post-apocalyptic Stillwater Bay, where narrative-driven gameplay unfolds through interactions with engaging NPCs and missions. <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/9f7ca1bf50eff816d8f55f780b7405c8.webp?t=1749555056\" width=600 height=49 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/86c2bf1b3f23e1d6c3b1955f12fd707b.poster.avif?t=1749555056\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/86c2bf1b3f23e1d6c3b1955f12fd707b.webm?t=1749555056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/419520/extras/86c2bf1b3f23e1d6c3b1955f12fd707b.mp4?t=1749555056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Gear up for a challenge, where you'll navigate through intense encounters that promise 